description: Assigns a farm membership level to a member.

parameters.name: farmId
parameters.description: The ID of the farm to associate with the member.

parameters.name: principalId
parameters.description: The member's principal ID to associate with the farm.

parameters.name: principalType
parameters.description: The principal type of the member to associate with the farm.

parameters.name: identityStoreId
parameters.description: The identity store ID of the member to associate with the farm.

parameters.name: membershipLevel
parameters.description: The principal's membership level for the associated farm.
